Definition: a grammatical category in inflected languages governing the agreement between nouns and pronouns and adjectives
Example: in some languages it is quite arbitrary but in Indo-European languages it is usually based on sex or animateness
Synonyms: grammatical_gender, grammatical_category, a, grammatical, category, in, inflected, languages, governing, the, agreement, between, nouns, and, pronouns, adjectives, some, it, is, quite, arbitrary, but, Indo-European, usually, based, on, sex, or, animateness
Category: noun.communication
